  "text": "language\nSkip to main content\nPRO\nPro indicator: A premium offering that requires a paid subscription.\nAmson安生｜數位行銷 x IG變現\nHome\nContacts\nAutomation\nManychat AI\nInbox\n2\nSettings\nMy Profile\nHelp\nSettings\nMain\nGeneral\nNotifications\nTeam Members\nLogs\nDisplay\nBilling\nSubscriptions\nInvoices\nPayment Details\nInbox\nInbox Behavior\nAuto-Assignment\nChannels\nInstagram\nTikTok\nWhatsApp\nMessenger\nSMS\nEmail\nTelegram\nAutomation\nFields\nTags\nConversion Events\nExtensions\nAPI\nApps\nIntegrations\nPayments\nInstalled Templates\nPixel\nInstagram\n@carry.digital.nomad\nDefault Reply\nSend\nInstagram Default Reply\nThe Default Reply is triggered when your contact types something your bot cannot recognize, like if you haven’t set up a Keyword. We recommend setting it up to welcome new contacts, give them more information, and give them a way to nagivate their conversation, in case they get lost.\nMain Menu\nEdit\nThe Main Menu is the “hamburger” menu located at the top right corner of Direct Messages. It can be opened at any time by your contacts. Customize it to give your contacts an easy way to navigate your bot.\nSay hi to new followersBETA\nUnavailable yet\nMeta limited the use of this functionality.\nGet more info\nA one-time welcome DM sent through Meta’s official API to new Instagram followers the moment they hit follow, but only the first time they do.\nConversation Starters\nEdit\nConversation Starters provide a way for users to start a conversation with a business with a list of frequently asked questions or discussion topics.\nOpt-in Automation\nEdit\nOpt-In triggers the automation when the user types \"Start\" or \"Subscribe\" in your Instagram channel. These system keywords are by default and aren't editable.\nOpt-out Automation\nEdit\nOpt-out triggers the automation when the user types \"Stop\" or \"Unsubscribe\" in your Instagram channel. These system keywords are by default and aren't editable.\nStory Mention Reply\nCreate New Reply\nSelect Existing\nStart an automation, like a message or Manychat Action, if someone mentions your Instagram account in their Story.\nAds Optimization\nMeta Conversions API\nConnect\nThe Conversions API is a Meta Business Tool that allows you to share data with Meta to enhance the performance of ads.\nLearn More\nOpen Event Manager\nRefresh Instagram Permissions\nRefresh Permissions\nInstagram can unexpectedly lose the connection to your page permissions. If you encounter any trouble, like content not sending or setting not saving, always refresh your permissions first.\nDisable Instagram Channel\nDisable\nYou can temporary disable Instagram Channel if you want to stop your automation. It can be enabled again later.\nLearn More\nRemove Instagram Account from Manychat\nRemove\nYou can completely remove Instagram account from Manychat if you want to connect another page or disable Instagram channel. Note: all your Instagram subscribers will be deleted from Manychat.",
